To  Copy  Google Drive shared file from My Drive.

1.   Create Shortcut Of Shared Folder To My Drive
2.   Connect Colab & wait for Connected status
3.   Mount Drive from left sidebar Folder Icon 
4.   Copy file location and paste in destination location 
5.   Create a code cell & paste that line 
        
             !sudo cp -v -r "Shared File location/" "Destination" 

6. Run the Cell
